column2: Independent housing units designed for individual households, the predominant form in private, single-occupancy neighborhoods.
Housing classification for structures designed to accommodate multiple separate dwelling units within a single building.
High-end, upscale living spaces with premium amenities, exceptional design, and exclusive features, offering a luxurious lifestyle.
A structure designed and designated for business and professional activities, providing office spaces and facilities for commercial enterprises.
A commercial structure designed for the sale of goods or provision of food services, catering to retail, dining, and dietary experiences.
Dedicated area equipped for food preparation, often utilized for professional catering services or large-scale culinary operations.
A facility designed for the storage, organization, and distribution of goods, serving as a central hub for inventory management and order fulfillment.
